WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Alpine weather creates amazing data patterns!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
We measure temperature, rainfall, and wind speed in the mountains.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Graphs and charts help us understand weather trends.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Mountain weather can change quickly and dramatically.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Let's explore the mathematics of alpine meteorology!